  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients on hemodialysis will be randomly assigned (1:1) to continue on conventional
      hemodialysis or on-line hemodiafiltration, both three times per week. A 3 year follow-up and
      a sample size of around 750 will be necessary to detect a 35% reduction in mortality.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
