  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 18 and older

          -  Currently undergoing hemodialysis

          -  Clinical stability

          -  Stable vascular access

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Chronic inflammatory diseases

          -  Liver cirrhosis

          -  Malignancies

          -  Chronic immunosuppressant or antiinflammatory use

          -  Dialysis through temporary catheter or single puncture
      </textblock>
